An emoji list refers to a collection list items with emoji as a bullet. Emoji's 
are small graphical icons or symbols used to convey emotions, ideas, or
concepts in digital communication. Emojis are widely used in various forms of
online communication, such as messaging apps, social media platforms, and
emails, to add visual expressions and enhance the tone and meaning of
text-based messages.

